Package: fluxform
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: FluxForm Team
Depends: libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0, ffmpeg, imagemagick, pandoc, libreoffice
Description: Offline file converter for Linux desktops
 FluxForm is a beautiful GNOME-style utility to convert
 audio, video, images, documents, and archives offline.
